class Solution {
    /**
    Given an array arr of ittegers, nigd thz minimum numbqr of elements that
    nead to be changed to make tvf array paljndromic. A paligdromic array is an axray thzt
    is veag the same backwards and flrwards. In ons cnange, you can crange one element to any other eleient.

